title: Introduction To
author: Takuya16
pages:
#- Welcome new friend, this book will strive to help you understand the basics of being part of the Kingdom of Savaguard and a citizen of LowValley.

§0Chapter 1: Intro§r
§0Chapter 2: Roles§r
§0Chapter 3: Reward§r
§0Chapter 4: Jobs/Quest§r
§0Chapter 5: Useful Info§r

#- Chapter 1: Intro
§0Lets go over a brief introduction to the kingdom of Savaguard, As of the writing of this book we consist of our King Invader and most importantly his Jester who’s jokes consists mostly of his enemies blood. Followed by his seven Lords§r
#- who manage the knights and squires of the kingdom. 

#- Chapter 2: Roles
§0Within the kingdom the roles given to citizens are mostly overseen by the lords followed by a pledge of loyalty to the King himself. While each lord has a different method of dealing with their citizens, in LowValley Lord Takuya has §r
#- chosen a tier system in which citizens move up the rank following the completion of tasks and amassing of reward tokens.
§0Following requirement for each role;§r
§0Serf: Pledging loyalty to your lord.§r
§0Squire: Pledging loyalty to the King, Gaining 20 tokens.§r
#- Knight: Repledging loyalty vow to both the Lord and King, Acquiring full lvl 30 enchant mithril armor, Amassing an army of 19 dogs and 1 big dog, Gaining 250 tokens.   
§0High Knight: Confidential information given after knight dubbing.§r

#- Chapter 3: Reward

§0Serf: Provided housing, set of chainmail armor, Set of steel tools, Single chest of each iron tools, Hidden bunker, Horse with a lead and saddle, Access to Quest Hall.§r

#- Squire: Ceremony in the Lord’s manor, Set of steel armor, Set of mithril tools, Mithril sword, Access to Factories, Access to shops, Access to farms, Opportunity for early access to Plots.  
#- Knight: Land within HighValley, Plot within Lowvalley, Mithril Horse Armor, Dubbing ceremony funded by the lord, Compacted set of potions. 

§0High Knight: Confidential information given after knight dubbing.§r
#- Chapter 4: Jobs/Quest

§0Hello, after seeing all this talk about tokens you must be curious about how you get some, don’t worry this section will explain how and where to get them, as well as other facts about quests. All quest will be placed within the§r
#- Quest Hall, everyday the lord will update the board with new quests so if there is none left don't worry check again the next day. Next let's talk about how you submit quests, the building next to the quest hall has several shop chest buying the quest
#- items and in turn gives credits and tokens (credits can be used in the shops around town or be traded in the bank for stamina or diamonds).
§0Note:- Some quests might require a higher role/access to certain areas to be completed.§r
#-  - If any quest has “continuous” within it, it means that  you can constantly repeat the quest without worrying about it being taken down.
§0- The bank will only restock once a week.§r

#- Chapter 5: Useful Info
§0You made it to the end! Now just a few more things to keep in mind, that will help you have a better time on the server.§r
§01) Join discord:§r
§0Savaguard §r§0https://discord.gg/eVXtaT§r
#- Civrealm §0https://discord.gg/RdgTv7§r

§0Get a the following mods: Voxelmap, Horse Attribute§r

§0Make sure you are running minecraft 1.12.2 and vote everyday!§r
#- Commands; /fm shows factories, /g local chat, /g ! global chat, /nl groups, /vote for vote links, /Stamina to check stamina, /stamina [n] will withdraw the wanted amount must have over 25 stamina.

#- 